{"tid":822781,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳 業 坤 自 爆 何 超 蓮 係 佢 個 Ex","createTime":"2018-09-16T13:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T02:02:14.000Z","uid":35964,"like":23,"dislike":1443,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"4a241e08eb565a50a82c5239ed183623a962af36","tid":822781,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"歌手吳業坤同JW（王灝兒）相當老友，之前仲一齊開過騷同出合唱歌，吳業坤喺老友面前自然特別鬆懈，仲唔小心爆咗自己料添！<br />\n<br />\n轉咗夢中情人<br />\n<br />\nJW尋日就喺IG上載咗段限時動態片，仲Tag埋好姊妹何超蓮，一開頭佢就問吳業坤：「你頭先話超蓮係你邊個話？你個Ex（前度）呀？」雖然吳業坤即刻嗌唔係，但JW就話：「你頭先話係你個Ex喎！」令對方急急澄清：「係Ex夢中情人！」之後被問到即係依家唔鍾意啦？吳業坤就話：「JW正啲！」令JW笑唔停，果然係溝女王呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180914/photo/bkn-20180914112355888-0914_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180914123055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180914%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180914112355888-0914_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180914123055&h=0f0226e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"778ddd6cb9abe5f8607da55bd38afdebfa759603","tid":822781,"uid":121997,"like":14,"dislike":1201,"score":-1187,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T13:23:01.000Z","msg":"'关你撚事咩"},{"pid":"783db1c61592bc38f7c6402c0a47786c495f2b73","tid":822781,"uid":132587,"like":1250,"dislike":4,"score":1246,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T13:23:04.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣人氣下滑速度比想像中快<br />\n以為果年原來他不夠愛我之後可以玩多一兩年<br />\n點知果年完左就收曬皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa93aa0c8cad4f9237287a194d5a04395ef833a","tid":822781,"uid":41974,"like":423,"dislike":5,"score":418,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T13:23:42.000Z","msg":"邊撚個吳業坤？"},{"pid":"e2e21f9fd5ebd64e6fead5c09951d57ce7009624","tid":822781,"uid":14423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"唔係啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73fe573b6854df8ee78b04e71b7aef30f479867","tid":822781,"uid":176657,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"rep